Upstairs is an open kitchen that effortlessly flows into the café and a family room with balcony access, ideal for indoor-outdoor living. Throughout the home is a total of three bedrooms and a top-floor loft for shared entertainment space. Interior photos disclosed are different from the actual model being built.
